# Welcome to %d easy steps to installing reblog

1. Download and install [Typesafe activator](https://typesafe.com/activator)
2. Run "activator dist"
3. Wait for a loooong time
4. While waiting, If you don't get the joke in the title, go and watch: [Spanish Inquisition Sketch](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vt0Y39eMvpI)
5. Copy the resulting zip file whereever you want to run the applcation
6. Unzip the stuff
7. If you want, configure some values in conf/ directory
8. Run the system by invoking ./bin/reblog
9. Be happy!
